entry.name: Community proteogenomics reveals insights into the physiology of phyllosphere bacteria
entry.description: PRIDE ID: 9856. [[http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/19805315 Proc Natl Acad Sci U S A. 2009 Sep 22;106(38):16428-33]]. Analyzed against all prokaryote proteomes currently available, as well as A. thaliana proteome.
